 "lrc": "[00:00.00]Mm.\n[00:01.92]This summer still feel different.\n[00:03.52]But this ain’t no vacation.\n[00:07.04]This is pressure.\n[00:08.32]This is fire.\n[00:09.60]This is where the void learns its name.\n[00:13.76]Build!\n[00:13.84]Rise!\n[00:15.68]Pressure make gold!\n[00:16.56]Pressure make more!\n[00:18.40]Ah ya ya\n[00:20.16]We outside now\n[00:25.28]Ah ya ya\n[00:25.28]Feet on the ground\n[00:25.28]Ah ya ya\n[00:27.12]Let the bass roll low\n[00:28.32]From the void to the gold\n[00:30.64]I had too much weight sitting heavy on my shoulders\n[00:36.96]Too many tabs in my mind, too many nights getting colder\n[00:40.56]Same walls, same clock, same fight with time\n[00:43.92]Same ghost in the room saying “you ain’t gon’ shine”\n[00:47.76]But the drums came in like a war call\n[00:49.52]Strings hit sharp, made the whole floor talk\n[00:51.28]One deep breath, then I stood up straight\n[00:52.96]Had to stop asking life when it’s my time to take\n[00:55.04]Laptop closed but the soul still loading\n[00:56.56]Hands still dirty but the heart still golden\n[01:00.72]I was down in the void with the lights gone low\n[01:03.52]Now I beat on the dark till the whole thing glow\n[01:08.00]I was not broken\n[01:08.80]I was being remade\n[01:09.28]I was not buried\n[01:12.64]I was under the flame\n[01:16.96]Empty out the fear\n[01:17.20]Fill the chest with fire\n[01:19.84]Step through the noise\n[01:22.00]Climb a little higher\n[01:24.56]No shame in the scars\n[01:26.88]No fear in the climb\n[01:28.80]If the world get loud around me\n[01:30.64]I’ma turn it into mine\n[01:32.80]We came from the void\n[01:34.32]Now we turn it into gold\n[01:36.00]Gold in the heart\n[01:36.72]Gold in the soul\n[01:36.72]Built from the pressure\n[01:36.72]Raised by the cold\n[01:36.72]We came from the void\n[01:36.72]Now we turn it into gold\n[01:36.72]Gold!\n[01:36.72]But we aiming past gold!\n[01:36.72]Gold!\n[01:36.72]Make the whole world know!\n[01:36.72]Oh-oh, let it burn\n[01:37.28]Oh-oh, let it show\n[01:37.47]Oh-oh, watch me grow\n[01:38.24]We came from the void\n[01:41.16]Now we turn it into gold\n[01:42.72]Mind clear\n[01:43.20]Heart bold\n[01:43.60]Hands up\n[01:43.68]Still gold\n[01:44.32]New me\n[01:44.32]Still loading\n[01:44.32]Soul clean\n[01:44.32]Still glowing\n[01:58.29]Cocktails and code used to sit on the table\n[02:15.20]Dreams in the blue screen, working when able\n[02:18.72]Now every line that I typed in pain\n[02:20.80]Came back strong with a brand-new name\n[02:22.24]No more waiting on permission\n[02:24.56]No more begging for a lane\n[02:26.40]No more hiding all the vision\n[02:28.32]No more making joy feel strange\n[02:30.08]They laughed when the tools came out\n[02:31.52]Said it ain’t real when the new wave sprout\n[02:33.28]But I built with the sparks, built with the scars\n[02:35.36]Built with the bass and I aimed at stars\n[02:37.20]You can call it slop, I call it seed\n[02:39.12]You can call it fake, I call it freed\n[02:41.12]You can throw shade, I let it mold\n[02:45.76]I came from the void and I turned it gold\n[02:47.60]I don’t need your crown\n[02:48.22]I don’t need your gate\n[02:49.60]I don’t need your doubt\n[02:51.28]I don’t need your weight\n[02:53.15]Have your joy but keep your spirit\n[02:54.80]Touch the flame but keep your name\n[02:56.16]Taste the world but don’t disappear in it\n[02:58.56]Pleasure don’t have to become pain\n[03:00.04]Pass the plate and pass forgiveness\n[03:03.61]Raise your glass and bless the air\n[03:03.68]We are only here a minute\n[03:04.90]Build the life you want while you here\n[03:38.80]We came from the void\n[03:38.85]Now we turn it into gold\n[03:39.03]Gold in the heart\n[03:39.16]Gold in the soul\n[03:39.20]Built from the pressure\n[03:39.20]Raised by the cold\n[03:39.39]We came from the void\n[03:39.75]Now we turn it into gold\n[03:40.18]Gold!\n[03:40.25]But we aiming past gold!\n[03:40.62]Gold!\n[03:40.69]Make the whole world know!\n[03:41.05]Oh-oh, let it burn\n[03:41.34]Oh-oh,